eu.linksmart.caf.cm.query
Class QueryRow

java.lang.Object
  eu.linksmart.caf.cm.query.QueryRow
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class QueryRow
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

A row of query results, from the Context Manager, as part of the QueryResponse. There is one QueryRow for each output defined - denoted by the rowID - in the ContextQuery the results are for.

Author:
Michael Crouch
